<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='380000' id='t-380000'>And this is clearly the story</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='382000' id='t-382000'>of the Chinese economic growth.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='385000' id='t-385000'>Let me look at this question more directly.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='387000' id='t-387000'>Is democracy bad for economic growth?</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='390000' id='t-390000'>Now let's turn to two countries,</span>
