<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='413000' id='t-413000'>as compared with $650 per capita GDP.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='417000' id='t-417000'>Both countries are in Asia.</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
 7:10
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='419000' id='t-419000'>If I were to ask you,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='421000' id='t-421000'>&quot;Which are the two Asian countries?</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='423000' id='t-423000'>And which one is a democracy?&quot;</span>
