<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='554000' id='t-554000'>So the East Asian model</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='556000' id='t-556000'>has this massive selection bias --</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='558000' id='t-558000'>it is known as selecting on a dependent variable,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='561000' id='t-561000'>something we always tell our students to avoid.</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
